d is trackable from the zone in by a druid or a ranger, pulling her is a pain tho lots adds heh have a good chanter is all i gotta say use the cleric spell lull it does help in pulling but you will still get id say around 6 adds <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#778899><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/udindadar.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Dindadar</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Monk-in-Training</span><br>  Posts: 69<br> <font color=#8b1a1a>(10/13/02 11:18:22 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fmonklybusiness43508frm7.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=5743.topic&index=2>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: HS</span><hr size=1> Shes a 3 day spawn (72 hours) with a 7 hour variance.  That means she can spawn anywhere from 65 hours to 79 hours from the time she is killed, just like the angry.  She can be tracked from zoneline by rangers and druids, but NOT bards.  I confirmed this personally when i took her down ;) had both a bard and a druid with me.  1 good group should be able to take her, shes really pretty easy.  Only tough part is getting to her.  Shes in the east hall, so theres 2 ways to get to her.  #1.  Get SOE (or sow and lev), and get on the fire pots near the south wing doors.  Run real quick over to the east hall, and you should be able to get up.  If you can't you have to go through the south hall.<br>
 <p>-Tyymm, 56th Enchanter<BR>
-Punches, 60th Monk<BR>
<a href=http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=220640>Punches Majelo Profile</a><CENTER></p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#cccccc><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/udnoel.showPublicProfile?language=EN>dnoel</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Monk</span><br>  Posts: 228<br> <font color=#8b1a1a>(10/14/02 3:46:03 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fmonklybusiness43508frm7.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=5743.topic&index=3>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: HS</span><hr size=1> Drusillia herself is trivial if you can get to her. I've gotten to her with just a 60 monk, 60 enc, and botting a 60 cleric.<br>
<br>
As for pulling her room, any 56+ monk that's not an E-bay shouldn't have any significant problem splitting it out. Just make sure the group is around the corner before the door to her room so you have room to work it.<br>
<br>
The golems in that room are a bit harder than anything else around, but nothing a 60 monk can't tank in under 2 cheals. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#778899><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/uvaleriusblacklung.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Valerius Blacklung</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Young Grasshoppah</span><br>  Posts: 3<br> <font color=#8b1a1a>(10/14/02 9:43:24 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fmonklybusiness43508frm7.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=5743.topic&index=4>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: HS</span><hr size=1> Great, thanks for the help guys.  I'm gonna have to start playing in HS more $$$ <p><a href=http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=305252>Brother Valerius Blacklung</a> <br> 60 Grandmaster <br> Guardians of the Keep <br> "Sol B is home"</p><i></i></td></tr></table><table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub35.ezboard.com/fmonklybusiness43508frm7.showPrevMessage?topicID=5743.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub35.ezboard.com/fmonklybusiness43508frm7.showNextMessage?topicID=5743.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br><a self href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fmonklybusiness43508frm7.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=5743.topic&index=4><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/professional/addReply.gif border=0 alt="Add Reply"></a> </td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fmonklybusiness43508frm7.emailToFriend?topicID=5743.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/email.gif border=0 alt="Email This To a Friend"> Email This To a Friend</a><br> <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fmonklybusiness43508frm7.threadControl?topicID=5743.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/professional/deleteThread.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control 